#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:156
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Here is the space of engineering.Despite the fact that the worlds of "
"Enginery are constantly attacked by mantes, you should get supplies for "
"travel."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:157
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You arrived in the engineering space.After the fall of the federation, "
"difficult times came for these mechanical creatures, but usually they try to"
" help."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:158
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You are entering the engineering space.These masters of engineering with "
"great joy will help the federation, however, in the current position, their "
"trust first needs to be earned."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:159
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"In this sector, many ships with developed drone technologies are "
"noticed.Perhaps they will help you break away from the rebels."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:160
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive in the once rather peaceful engine of the engineering.These "
"mechanized organisms can also paste the hull of your ship.For the "
"corresponding fee, of course."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:161
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"\"Welcome!\"- says the inscription on the lighthouse.All nothing, but binary"
" code?!Oh, these engineers ..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:162
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"Inji have always been loyal to the allies of the Federation.They are ready "
"to help even now, when the chances of victory are extremely small ..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:163
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[8]"
msgstr ""
"You arrived in the engine belonging to the engine.This race is famous for "
"its engineering skill, so if you still have not thought about the repair and"
" replenishment of supplies, now is the right time."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:164
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[9]"
msgstr ""
"Engi are a race of robots, where each humanoid \"unit\" consists of hundreds"
" of trillions of nanobots. They are the Federation's closest allies and very"
" peaceful by nature. They prefer research and practical utility over "
"everything else."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:172
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ENGI\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Inzhi can do amazing things from a pile of rubbish.The engineering base at "
"this lighthouse just sells such equipment."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:173
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ENGI\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The message comes: \"Our weapons, your scrap metal.\"You charge the shields,"
" but you understand that this is just an engineer of the engineer who offers"
" a deal."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:174
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ENGI\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"The engine's ship welcomes: “Improving the engines is necessary to travel "
"home.The sale of equipment is necessary to improve engines. ”"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:185
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Complex interweaving of ship hulls and cells of FTL drives swim, abandoned "
"by all in open space.Everything indicates that the engineers were here not "
"so long ago.But now there is no one here ..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:186
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive on a green planet with luxurious meadows and rolling "
"waterfalls.This place must not be interested in engineering."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:187
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You were next to the construction site of the engine.Most of the fibers out "
"of habit supports their two -legged appearance, but you see several hives of"
" the engineering engine that jointly work on the creation of massive organic"
" machines specializing in the construction of ships.It looks truly "
"grandiose."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:188
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"Although every “individual” of the engineering and consists of trillions of "
"nanomashi, their culture still rotates around traditional social "
"interactions.Nearby is a station, apparently built for the entertainment of "
"travelers."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:189
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"Nearby you see a number of space stations and Fleets of the engine.Although "
"they look like piles of random rubbish, they are in reality the standard of "
"effectiveness.Just in their buildings there is not enough element of "
"aesthetics."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:190
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"The system seems quite peaceful.However, you are not sure whether this is "
"for a long time: both the rebels and mantis threaten her at the same time."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:191
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"Through this area, despite the threat of mantis invasion, many merchant "
"ships pass.Without a doubt, there is demand for effective engine technology."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:192
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[8]"
msgstr ""
"You see a small carrier of the rebels in the distance.You hide and try to "
"mix with other ships.Nevertheless, it is amazing to see a military ship of "
"the rebels, moving alone in the depths of the engine's space."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:193
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[9]"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the engineers avoid specifically this node, in fact, like any "
"other forms of life.You look for the reasons for this, but the FTL drive "
"starts without incident."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:194
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[10]"
msgstr ""
"The cluster of engineers of the engineering in the orbit of the nearest "
"planet is the only hint that this mechanical appearance has ever been "
"here.You have other places to visit."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:214
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You are welcomed by the engine engine: “Identification: federation?Probably "
"outsider.It is assumed ... recovery.It is assumed ... Hope.Help is offered. "
"\"They provide you with some materials."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:215
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You intersect with an engine's cargo ship, which is in a hurry to get home "
"before the mantis fleet tries to capture this sector.They are happy to give "
"part of their cargo to get home quickly."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:216
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You establish contact with the Ingozh Separate Scientific Station, which "
"remained here, despite the likelihood of mantis invasion.They offer you to "
"experience some kind of experimental technology."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:217
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"It was a place of recent battle.Whoever appears here, mantis or engineering,"
" they were not inclined to go peacefully.You make your way through the "
"wreckage."

