"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"MOTILEK_RED_EVENT_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Upon appearing at the beacon, you come under attack by an insectoid-like "
"ship of an unknown species. You have no choice but to fight."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8368
