"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"MOTILEK_RED_EVENT_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"No one can say exactly where the insectors came from, but they are always "
"programmed to attack.And your meeting today is no exception ..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8369
