"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"MOTILEK_RED_EVENT_TEXT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You've heard of insectoids and their aggressive nature before, but never "
"about the species you've encountered this time. Nevertheless, it wants to "
"destroy you..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8373
msgid ""
