"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"morph\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Once on board, they easily find the AI cores but cannot deactivate them. The"
" Morph decides to quickly connect to the cores, destroying their own mind..."
" but also the AI!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8453
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"morph\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Now that the station is safe, you can inspect it in detail. You discover its"
" inhabitants have long been dead, but you manage to find one survivor who "
"wants to join your crew. You leave, taking whatever you find useful from the"
" station."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8463
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"anaerobic_crew\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Lanius crew member) Your Lanius has a suggestion on how to resolve the "
"situation."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8465
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"anaerobic_crew\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Lanius moves forward, opening an airlock toward the station. Its "
"metabolism emits no heat signature, making it invisible to the station's "
"defense systems."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8469
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"anaerobic_crew\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Once on board, it easily finds the AI cores and starts consuming them. "
"During your thorough search amidst the horrible scenes, it manages to find a"
" lone survivor."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8477
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"magman\""
