#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8497
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[7]/text"
msgstr "We cannot do anything about this."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8499
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MAD_ORCHID_STATION\"]/choice[7]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"After considering your options, you realize none of them are suitable for a "
"safe intervention. You switch to the next jump plan and discuss it with the "
"crew."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8507
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ION_BOARDER_MAD_STATION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You dock with the station and discover its inhabitants have long been dead. "
"You leave with a small amount of useful gear and horrible scenes in your "
"memory."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8511
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ION_BOARDER_MAD_STATION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You dock with the station and discover its inhabitants have long been dead. "
"You leave with a small amount of useful gear and horrible scenes in your "
"memory."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8515
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ION_BOARDER_MAD_STATION\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"You dock with the station and discover its inhabitants have long been dead. "
"You leave with some useful gear and horrible scenes in your memory."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8519
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ION_BOARDER_MAD_STATION\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"You dock with the station and discover its inhabitants have long been dead. "
"After gathering everything useful, you discover a small escape pod in which "
"you find a survivor."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8524
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ION_BOARDER_MAD_STATION\"]/event[5]/text"
msgstr ""
"The station AI sends automatic units to counter your drone. However, this "
"distraction allows your team to conduct a quick search, as a result of which"
" you find a survivor."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8531
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_ORCH_STATION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The AI defense system proved to be more advanced than your Engi could "
"imagine. You bring them back before the situation gets out of control."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8534
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_ORCH_STATION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Once on board, the Engi easily finds the AI cores and quickly wipes all "
"programs and deactivates the systems. During your thorough search amidst the"
" horrible scenes, you manage to find a lone survivor."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8542
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"MAGMAN_1_ORCH_STATION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Once on board, the Magmen tries several times to start a fire, but without "
"success. They quickly leave before finding themselves in a difficult "
"position."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8545
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"MAGMAN_1_ORCH_STATION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Once on board, the Magmen tries to start a fire, and after several attempts,"
" they manage to create a flame. You discover the station's inhabitants have "
"long been dead, but one of them survived."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8553
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"MAGMEN_2_ORCH_STATION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Once on board, the Magmen start a huge fire inside; the flames quickly melt "
"all sensors. Convinced no one is alive, they leave the station before it "
"explodes."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8557
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"MAGMEN_2_ORCH_STATION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Once on board, the Magmen start a huge fire inside; the flames quickly melt "
"all sensors. They discover a lone survivor, and they all leave the station "
"together before it explodes."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8581
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"While trying to get away from the Rebel fleet, you jump into the Orchid "
"sector. Despite the name given by humans, Orchids have little in common with"
" Earth plants."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8582
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Earthlings' first contact with Orchids occurred on their home planet, where "
"our researcher was eaten by a giant predatory flower."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8583
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids produce pure oxygen with a light scent, very similar to the scent of"
" Earth orchids."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8584
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"Despite the Rebels' general xenophobia toward other races, they sometimes "
"use Orchids as houseplants."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8585
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids fly semi-organic ships. Biologists who studied them claim that every"
" hit on an Orchid ship is felt as slight pain by the crew."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8586
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"Surprisingly, Orchid weapon production looks very similar to growing "
"vegetables in Earth greenhouses."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8587
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids really dislike it when other life forms change their ideal indoor "
"temperature (28-30C)."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8588
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ORCHID\"]/text[8]"
msgstr ""
"The main activity of Orchids in the Galaxy is related to the trade and "
"transport of food products, fertilizers, and medical preparations."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8597
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ORCHID\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"On this beacon there is a large shopping center of orchids.Despite the fact "
"that most of their equipment is made of plant materials, orchids are also "
"used for scrap metal and are ready to trade it."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8598
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ORCHID\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"A giant trading station of orchids under the protection of several warships "
"is located right near the lighthouse.You join and go to the station.You are "
"amazing how quiet and calm inside."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8599
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ORCHID\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"The lonely trading ship of the orchids is waiting for you at the "
"lighthouse.His team sends you a simple message: \"Weapons at affordable "
"prices.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8600
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ORCHID\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You came across a trading station of orchids selling consumer goods made of "
"organic materials.Upon learning what you represent the federation, the "
"orchids agree to sell weapons."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8610
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ORCHID\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The sectors of the orchids are famous for a calm, peaceful character.This "
"lighthouse confirms this."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8611
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ORCHID\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The lighthouse serves exclusively for transit.You notice how far from the "
"local star it is located.Probably in order to protect against solar "
"outbreaks."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8612
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ORCHID\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You reach a lighthouse located next to the planet, located in the process of"
" terraforming to support the life of plants.There are no ships around."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8613
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ORCHID\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"Now nothing happens on this lighthouse.The star is too dull to provide "
"energy to the form of life depending on the light."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8623
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_DRONE\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Due to the fact that the orchids are fragile and vulnerable, they often "
"resort to the use of drones to help in the management of ships.A drone "
"factory is located on the lighthouse, and still loyal federations.The "
"engineers of the orchids offer one of their creations for free."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8624
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_DRONE\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The cargo ship of the orchids is waiting at the lighthouse.As soon as you "
"complete the maneuver, they send a message after the message: “There is too "
"much cargo.I can't move.Please take this. \""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8625
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_DRONE\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"While the FTL drive is charging, you decide to explore the surface of a "
"nearby planet.In the foliage of a giant tree, you find a discharged drone, "
"probably left by pirates."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8632
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_WEAPON\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You are surprised by discovering the secret station of the Federation in the"
" depths of the territory of the orchids.Her team went so far that she hid "
"the base using her favorite materials of orchids: leaves and bark.The allies"
" offer a gun that should help in your journey."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8633
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_WEAPON\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The colony of orchids on a nearby planet agrees to give you a gun in "
"exchange for several rare plant samples from your native planet, which you "
"are lucky enough to transport in the hold."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8634
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_WEAPON\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you make a jump, the ship of orchids nearby explodes for an "
"unknown reason.All that remains after the explosion is molten metal "
"fragments and one non -judged gun."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8641
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FREE_ITEMS\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The generous orchids from the station on the lighthouse offer scrap metal "
"for free.“We don't need it.We prefer a titanium tree. \""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8642
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FREE_ITEMS\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The lighthouse is empty, there are no ships or stars around.A lonely "
"container, reminiscent of a giant seed in shape, drifts in space.Inside "
"there are slightly scrap metal and other useful resources."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8643
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FREE_ITEMS\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
