#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9013
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pay to visit the \"Flower Alley\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9015
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The exhibit contains an alley with a variety of local flowers. While walking"
" through it, you yawn and fall asleep on a bench..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9022
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"...you wake up from leaves hitting your face from some Orchid! They make it "
"clear they want to join your crew. You take them and leave."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9029
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Pay to visit the \"Organic Factory\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9031
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The exhibit is a workshop for producing Orchid drone equipment. The Orchid "
"tour guide talks about how healthy juice from organic drones is, besides "
"their primary functions."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9038
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"When the tour guide is distracted, you manage to pocket a drone schematic."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9045
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Pay to visit the \"Contemplation Stones\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9047
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you is a circle of stones on which sit creatures resembling Earth "
"meerkats, but with very intelligent faces. You feel they want you to sit "
"next to them..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9054
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"...after sitting next to the meerkats, you receive hidden knowledge about "
"the nearest stars."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9061
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_2\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Do not visit anything."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9068
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pay to visit the \"Strange Clearing\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9070
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The exhibit contains a clearing where some incomprehensible manipulations of"
" vines, tree roots, and leaves are constantly taking place..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9077
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"...you enthusiastically watch the process, and in the end, something "
"resembling a ship augmentation falls at your feet. By the way, the Rebels "
"have gotten closer in the meantime."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9085
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Pay to visit the \"Nitro-cucumber Greenhouse\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9087
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You walk between ripe cucumbers, and having picked one, are already about to"
" take a bite when one of the Orchids knocks the cucumber out of your hand "
"and throws you to the ground..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9094
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"...a deafening explosion rings out! Dusting yourself off, the Orchid "
"explains that these cucumbers are essentially biological munitions and gives"
" you a few as a gift."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9103
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Pay to visit the \"Mushroom Cluster\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9105
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You enter a rather dark room where, in the dim light, you see endless rows "
"of mushroom farms..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9112
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"...suddenly, a young mushroom hops up to you and, with signs, declares that "
"you are now on his team to save the Federation, and no refusals are "
"accepted."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9119
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_BOTANICAL_GALLERY_3\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Do not visit anything."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9126
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are surprised when you see the ship with a system in a system, mainly "
"inhabited by the orchids.Slaves opened the encrypted channel for "
"communication and invite you to join."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9129
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Talk to the lumps."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9131
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“Hello, two -legged Mussu bag.We led out such a long -term exsense during "
"the ssstoil.We are very sorry, but you are the most ugly person in the "
"galaxy, and you deserve to be embalmed and put up at the museum.Fighting to "
"imagine what your mother looks like. \""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9133
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Open fire!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9135
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You shoot at the ship with a saber, but they deftly evade.Captain Sagov "
"sends a disaster message to the neighboring planet of the orchids, claiming "
"that the pirates attacked him.To your surprise, orchids open fire from all "
"planetary defense tools on your ship.All this was part of the insidious plan"
" of the signs."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9137
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"CREW_ORCHID\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Orchid crew member) Have the Orchid explain to their brethren that Slugs "
"are trying to use them."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9139
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"CREW_ORCHID\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Orchids from the planet, after listening to your Orchid, point the PDS "
"at the Slugs."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9154
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Stop the communication session."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9160
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SLUG_TAUNT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Refuse and talk with the crew during charging the FTL drive."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9170
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The hostile ship of orchids is waiting for you at the lighthouse.Without a "
"single word, they open fire."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9171
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids in the lighthouse behave unusually aggressively.One of the ships "
"moves in your direction, preparing tools for a salvo.Scanning shows that "
"their crew is infected with alien parasites."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9172
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"The warship of the orchids is approaching and scanning your ship.Having "
"discovered that you are armed, the orchids charge the guns to protect their "
"territory."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9173
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIGHT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"The verbose ship of orchids sends you a message at the message: “We learned "
"that you, aliens, eat plants after preparing them on fire!You will be "
"punished for this crime! ”"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9174
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIGHT\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"The ship of orchids awaits you at the lighthouse.An ominous message appears "
"on the screen for negotiations: \"In this world ... kill or you will be "
"killed.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9179
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SURRENDER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Accept an offer."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9186
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_SURRENDER\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "No mercy to the enemies!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9191
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_SURRENDER\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The ship of orchids turns off all the guns, hoping that you will do the "
"same."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9192
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_SURRENDER\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The ship of orchids is almost destroyed.His team sends you images "
"symbolizing the world and valuable cargo, probably with a request to "
"surrender."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9193
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_SURRENDER\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids on the screen are desperately waved with leaves and hollow the stems"
" on the keyboard.After a few seconds, you get a message, a complete typo: "
"“MVA SDLEMSHYA, Probtatitis Fire!”"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9200
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids make tremendous efforts to maintain security in their worlds, but "
"the lonely pirate still managed to break through even through their "
"defense.Do not avoid battles."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9201
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Orchid sectors are considered relatively safe and attract merchants and "
"refugees.Those, in turn, attract pirates."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9202
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"A ship with a pirate skull on the hull is waiting for you at the "
"lighthouse.You eavesdrop on the conversation on their ship: “This is not a "
"space grass.Doesn't matter.Fire\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9203
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FIGHT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You enjoyed the view of the planet of orchids overgrown with jungle, as a "
"pirate suddenly appeared from nowhere.The conflict is inevitable."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9210
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_ROCK_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Rock ships are often found in orchid sectors.Despite their hostility to the "
"aliens, the rocks are highly appreciated by orchids.The ship at the "
"lighthouse, however, behaves hostile to you."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9211
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_ROCK_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids find rocks with very useful allies for their ability to confront "
"fire, and given how easy it is to manipulate them.The ship’s ship at the "
"lighthouse regards you as a threat to their vegetable lords and attacks!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9212
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_ROCK_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"Orchid sectors are very popular among wealthy roks travelers.The body, "
"overgrown with rare plants, is considered fashionable in the culture of "
"fats.The ship at the lighthouse believes that you look menacing and "
"attacking."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9219
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_MANTIS_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Militia mantles send their ships throughout the galaxy in order to hunt "
"other ships for the sake of prey and glory.Orchid sectors are no exception."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9220
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_MANTIS_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Orchids make enormous efforts to peaceful mantles and establish a warmer "
"relationship with them.But some mantes will never leave the war path.The "
"ship at the lighthouse belongs to just that."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9221
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_MANTIS_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"Some mantes were so susceptible to the influence of orchids that they "
"worship plants and do the only thing that, in their opinion, will please "
"their gods: they kill all strangers."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9228
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_REBEL_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The rebel fighter awaits you at the lighthouse.An image of an officer-man "
"appears on the screen: “We came to hide this sector from aliens and "
"supporters of the federation.Let's start with you! \""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9229
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_REBEL_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The aggressively tuned ship of the rebels chose a lighthouse away from the "
"main worlds of orchids to wait for your possible arrival.As soon as the "
"rebels saw you, the ship immediately came into motion with charged tools."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9230
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_REBEL_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"This lighthouse was marked as populated by the Archids by allies on star "
"maps, but the fleet of the rebels has already begun to capture it.One of the"
" reconnaissance ships of the rebels attacks."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9237
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Upon learning that many ships of the Federation use the family of orchids as"
" a shelter, the rebels sent drones to hunt for everyone who confronts the "
"uprising.One of these ships is waiting for you at the lighthouse."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9238
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The unmanned ship broadcasts the message: “Any existence of plants is "
"prohibited.Only people are allowed in this sector.Glory to the uprising. "
"\"He is hostile to everyone except the rebels."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9239
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"The remains of the civilian ship of the orchids are dripping at the "
"lighthouse.The culprit, the unmanned ship of the rebels, unfolds and moves "
"towards you, while charging the guns."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9246
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_CAPTURED_REBEL_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You are surprised by hearing the crew of the orchid ship saying in a human "
"voice: “Give up.All nearby worlds are controlled by the uprising "
"forces.Resistance is useless. \""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9247
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_CAPTURED_REBEL_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The ship of orchids behaves more aggressively than usual.Scanning shows that"
" the ship is captured by people in the uniforms of the rebels."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9248
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_CAPTURED_REBEL_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"The ship of the orchids, located at the lighthouse, moves back and forth.The"
" rebels who captured the ship have not yet learned how to manage it, but are"
" already attacking you."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9261
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FRIENDLY_ASB\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A pirate ship, touched in numerous battles, moves in your direction because "
"of the planet of orchids.Maybe it's time to check how well the orchids "
"monitor the safety of their systems?"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9264
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FRIENDLY_ASB\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Fight with a pirate one on one."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9268
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FRIENDLY_ASB\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ask for help."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9270
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ORCHID_PIRATE_FRIENDLY_ASB\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You send a distress signal, and the military base of the orchids located on "
"the planet immediately responds and uses the planetary defense system "
"against the pirates."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:9280
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ORCHID_BOSS_REW1\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Their prototype was not injured in battle, and you transfer it to your ship."

